fulltitle: Chomsky's Statements on the JFK Assassination: Two Critiques
title: Chomsky's Statements on the JFK Assassination: Two Critiques
_filename: _Chomsky's Statements on the JFK Assassination - Two Critiques.webm
description:
For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub

Following Chomsky's short statement on the JFK assassination, this video presents responses from two well known personalities on the left - Michael Parenti (author) and John Judge (assassination researcher and anti-war activist).

Chomsky Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=liS-Rl1Fx6c
Full Michael Parenti Talk: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FkSJBffuxBM
Full John Judge Talk: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRrhEaPJ0_A
